wmsLayer.name: Macquarie_UTM58S_100m
wmsLayer.title: Macquarie UTM58S 100m
wmsLayer.description: This layer contains all processed multibeam bathymetry data that is publically available at Geoscience Australia, around Macquarie Ridge within UTM Zone 58 South. Data is gridded at 100 metres resolution. The colour ramp for the WMS is stretched between 300-6500 metres water depth. The dataset can be downloaded at the following URL http://services.ga.gov.au/metadata-gateway/metadata/record/73697.
